<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_54" id="26v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l1">Regenſpurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_54_r3l2">Lieben <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt / <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Hallaw<ex>er</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / wie <expan>ew<ex>er</ex></expan> CƷöllner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r3l3">beÿ ew cʒol an Jn gevoꝛdert hab / <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> cʒöllner ſchicken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r3l4">vnd beſtellen wöllet / daʒ er den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> / vnd ander vnſer Burger mit ſölichen voꝛ = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r3l5"><expan>derunge<ex>n</ex></expan> vmbeſwert laʒ / vvann wir von alter alſo gefreÿet / vnd <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r3l6">daʒ die vnſeren des beÿ ew überhaben ſein ſüllen / das wöllen etc antvvurt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r3l7"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria <expan>Sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> poſt Martinj Anno etc Nono $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_54" id="26v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Regenspurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat
                                                fürgelegt <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Hallaw<ex>er</ex></expan>, unser
                                                  <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>er</ex></expan> czöllner bey ew czol
                                                an in gevordert hab.
                                                <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> czöllner schicken und
                                                bestellen wöllet, daz er den
                                                  <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> und ander unser
                                                burger mit sölichen
                                                  vor<expan>derunge<ex>n</ex></expan> umbeswert laz,
                                                wann wir von alter also gefreyet und
                                                  <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, daz die
                                                unseren des bey ew überhaben sein süllen. Das wöllen
                                                etc. Antwurt. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria
                                                  <expan>sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> post Martini anno
                                                etc. nono.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
